name: make
description:
Builds a `NonEmptyArray` from an non-empty collection of elements.
*Example
documentation:
Builds a `NonEmptyArray` from an non-empty collection of elements.
*Example**

```ts
import { Array } from "effect"

const result = Array.make(1, 2, 3)
console.log(result) // [1, 2, 3]
```
